The Silver Daggers <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CBC6B1><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uarkianus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arkianus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#8E9173>(7/17/00 4:30:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsevents.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=83.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 5/17/00 PoF Recap</span><hr size=1> I had a blast on the raid. <br>
